{"title":"Initial Impressions: An Adidas Velosamba Unboxed Review","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/03/initial-impressions-an-adidas-velosamba-unboxed-review/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=initial-impressions-an-adidas-velosamba-unboxed-review","date":1615922391000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-207201\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"Initial Impressions: An Adidas Velosamba Unboxed Review\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>A few weeks ago, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2021/03/adidas-new-velosamba-marks-a-return-to-the-classic-adidas-cycling-shoe/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Adidas announced</a> the new <a href=\"https://www.adidas.com/us/the-velosamba-cycling-shoes/FW4459.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Velosamba</a> “commuter” shoes. I jumped on them as soon as the press release hit our inbox and I must say, I’m impressed. Read on for a more detailed look as well as some initial impressions…<span id=\"more-207201\"></span></p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>One critique I heard from people who hadn’t even seen these shoes in person is that the cleat would sit proud of the sole, causing an annoying tapping as you’d walk. The truth is, these cleats are well recessed in the gum sole.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-6.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-7.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>With reflective strips, as well as a reflective logo on the heel, these will make for a great commuter shoe. As far as stiffness. They aren’t road shoes but I’d say they’re as stiff as my XC/trail mountain bike shoes. Adidas made these for commuters but I’m planning on riding them on my mountain bike.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>Sambas are an icon and the Velosambas look <em>very</em> close to the OG shoes. They do feel more secure and robust. Like they were beefed up a bit for their job. Adidas makes fine footwear and the detailing reflects that. There is no excess glue or hardness in the suede. The soles look durable and the fit is spot on. These really are a grand effort by the brand to solidify its dedication to making superior athletic wear.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/AdidasVelosamba-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>The Velosambas sold out immediately but Adidas is restocking them. They’ll be a staple within its lineup and this shouldn’t come as a surprise seeing as how Adidas bought FiveTen a few years back and has been steadily building its cycling product line up to be a part of its athletics catalog.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.adidas.com/us/the-velosamba-cycling-shoes/FW4459.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Adidas Velosamba</a><br>Retail: $120.00<br>Size shown here: 12US</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"5605096246129a95bf4342c7bc7d6429d8af30846724f7b80b81b0e1587cb746","category":"Cycling"}